<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id4cbfc242-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d" identifier="/us/usc/t34/s10425"><num value="10425">§ 10425.</num><heading> Evaluation</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Each State that receives a grant under this subchapter shall submit to the Attorney General an evaluation not later than March 1 of each year in such form and containing such information as the Attorney General may reasonably require.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id4cbfc243-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d">(<ref href="/us/pl/90/351/tI/s1905">Pub. L. 90–351, title I, § 1905</ref>, as added <ref href="/us/pl/103/322/tIII/s32101/a/3">Pub. L. 103–322, title III, § 32101(a)(3)</ref>, <date date="1994-09-13">Sept. 13, 1994</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/108/1900">108 Stat. 1900</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id4cbfc244-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id4cbfc245-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I76" topic="codification" id="id4cbfc246-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Codification</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section was formerly classified to <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s3796ff–4">section 3796ff–4 of Title 42</ref>, The Public Health and Welfare, prior to editorial reclassification and renumbering as this section.</p>
</note>
</notes>
